\tc2 25
\tc3 \bdit 3 Sion\bdit* - Eiloheh Sion mutisi
\tr 
\tc1 90
\tc2 4
\tc3 \bdit Sion\bdit* - Eiloheh Sion mutisi
\tr 
\tc1 95
\tc2 ZF
\tc3 Avuli kat eiloheh Sion ka alingi en mari eim takeih en aelan ten out Patmos.
\tr 
\tc1 95
\tc2 27
\tc3 \bdit Revelesen\bdit* - Eiloheh Sion mutisi en eim takeih e out Patmos.
\tr 
\tc1 100
\tc2 ZG
\tc3 \bd Eiloheh Sion\bd*, apuruni en oel koa mutin. Romattei ka purun varein aven. Ka mat esuk navong matu revi. 
